Ray Roman Construction Page Clone

This project is a clone of the Ray Roman Construction landing page, built to practice frontend development and UI/UX skills. The goal was to replicate the design, layout, and responsiveness of the original website using clean, modern web technologies.

🚀 Features

Responsive layout for desktop and mobile

Clean and minimal UI design

Structured with semantic HTML5

Styled using CSS3 (Flexbox/Grid for layout)

Smooth hover effects and transitions

SEO-friendly code structure

🛠️ Tech Stack

HTML5 – for semantic and structured markup

CSS3 – for styling, layouts, and animations

JavaScript (optional) – for interactive elements

📂 Project Structure
├── index.html       # Main page  
├── style.css        # Stylesheet  
├── /assets          # Images, icons, and media files  
└── README.md        # Project documentation  

🎯 Purpose

This project is purely for educational purposes and showcases my ability to replicate professional landing page designs from scratch.

